                    Expert in <strong>AWS, Azure, and SAP BTP</strong> platforms with deep command of <strong>.NET / C#</strong>
                    and SAP development — integrating systems across banking, payments, supply chain, and data platforms.
                    Proven technical leader adept at Agile workflows, advanced design principles, and building reliable,
