                    architected a <strong>Payments-as-a-Service</strong> platform at Finexio (fintech) and led enterprise
                    SAP + Azure integrations at <strong>Nestlé</strong> for over a decade across Brazil, Missouri, and remote.
                    Implemented <strong>Generative AI</strong> via Amazon Bedrock in production.
                </p>
                <p class="about-body">Bilingual English / Portuguese. US Citizen. Austin, TX.</p>
